name: Test that setting a local variable will override a global variable
scenarioId: tiger-test-lib/TigerGlueTest_secondFile:Test that setting a local variable will override a global variable
methodName: Test that setting a local variable will override a global variable

testSteps.description: Given TGR set local feature variable "tiger.tigerGlue.helloTestFeature2" to "local value feature 2nd file"
Given TGR set local variable "tiger.tigerGlue.helloTestLocal" to "local value 2nd file"
Then TGR assert variable "tiger.tigerGlue.helloTestLocal" matches "local value 2nd file"
Then TGR assert variable "tiger.tigerGlue.helloTestFeature1" matches "global value for helloTestFeature1"
Then TGR assert variable "tiger.tigerGlue.helloTestFeature2" matches "local value feature 2nd file"

title: Test that setting a local variable will override a global variable
